---
// Problem.astro
---
<section class="problem section section-light">
  <div class="container problem-container">
    <h2>Empowering every child to read independently.</h2>
    <div class="problem-body">
      <p>
        Children with dyslexia deserve the same access to learning as their peers. When educational materials are designed with equity in mind, barriers to reading disappear. Dyslexia Reader provides the tools your child needs to build essential literacy skills, access grade-level content, and achieve lasting classroom success.
      </p>
      <p class="highlight">
        It's time to level the playing field. What if the book met your child halfway?
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    padding: var(--spacing-24) 0;
  }

  .problem-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);
  }

  .problem-body p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .problem-body .highlight {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-6);
  }
</style>
